snippet.textDisplay:
LOONA's random worldwide accomplishments:
-FIRST Korean girl group (and one of the first girl groups in history) to get a #1 single & #1 album on iTunes USA!!
-collabed w/ Grimes
-Yves is Sunmi's SUPER successful fan (srsly Sunmi likes every Yves post that people send her way)
-Haseul is Jo Sumi’s successful fan
-acknowledged by Oh My Girl (Gowon's a successful fan), 9MUSES’ Sera (Yeojin was noticed <3), Hyomin, Martha Stewart, Charli XCX, slayyyter, Soya, CLC’s Eunbin
-played on TV in Brazil, Indonesia, Argentina, Netherlands
-exists in Overwatch according to Michael Chu (who’s a fan), Widowmaker's canon fave member is Yves
-Eclipse was in NASA's playlist
-LOONA songs played in H&M's in US, France
-MTV EMA award for Best Korean Act; Yeojin's the youngest EMA winner ever
-artistry acknowledged by Billboard, Teen Vogue, MTV (incl. MTV Brazil)
-LDN Noise wants to collab
-that Chuuves meme took OFF
-Janelle Monae wants to collab <3
-admired by GWSN (also friends), Dreamnote, Busters, Pristin’s Kyla & Hinapia’s Eunwoo, BVNDIT’s Jungwoo, BDC’s Junghwan, Conan Gray
-friends with WJSN, Itzy, DIA, Momoland, fromis_9, The Boyz, Iz*one, Cherry Bullet, Astro, Elris
-love4eva hand choreo done by Dreamcatcher’s Yoohyeon & Siyeon and A.C.E’s Jun (boy group w/ the most rights)
-XX hit #1 in 34 countries; third Korean girl group album to top iTunes USA after RV & Twice
-++ and XX sold 100K copies total for their debut
-one of the first groups to explicitly acknowledge and provide support for LGBTQ fans <3 + tons of LOONA fans at Pride events around the world (:
-the 'Chuu heart' went viral and is now done by a lot of idols
-worked with NCT’s Cherry Bomb choreographer, who praised their skills; another SM choreographer wants them to cover Love Shot; Haechan watched their Cherry Bomb cover & said LOONA did it better (thanks lol)
-Hyunmin’s maybe a fan of Kim Lip lol?
-Chuu’s pic subtly referenced in a popular Korean webcomic
-Cocomong (animation) official social media posted about Kim Lip
-MTN’s Special Award for CF Star Rookies
-viral LCM idol edits, and fantastic edits w/ their discography all around, incl. one Khalid noticed
-first group to sell out merch at KCON 2019, plus LOONACON in general
-Soribada Performance Award
-SNH48 (Shanghai-based girl group) covered Butterfly
-JinsoulBlackHair, LOONAAA trended high in multiple countries on twitter
-brand endorsement by a popular school uniform company
-first girl group to win the AAA popularity vote
-a great Filipino speed skater said ‘stan loona’ during the SEA Games 2019 :P
-The Carol is the highest charting Korean Christmas song on iTunes USA
